### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Crear proveedor
POST {{host}}/api/providers
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "nombre": "Proveedor Ejemplo",
  "ruc": "1799999999001"
}
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Listar activos
GET {{host}}/api/providers?q=ejemplo&page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Listar incluyendo inactivos (soft-deleted)
GET {{host}}/api/providers?q=&page=1&pageSize=10&includeInactive=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Editar (PUT) — cambia el :id por uno real devuelto en "Crear" o "Listar"
PUT {{host}}/api/providers/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "nombre": "Proveedor Actualizado",
  "ruc": "1799999999001"
}

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Inactivar (soft delete) — deja active=false
DELETE {{host}}/api/providers/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Restaurar (PATCH) — vuelve a active=true
PATCH {{host}}/api/providers/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "active": true
}
